creator: Louisa May Alcott
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 16 readings of A Song from the Suds, by Louisa May Alcott, author of novels like Little Women. This was the fortnightly poem for June 7-21, 2015. Read in English by Chris Pyle; Domenica Campbell; David Lawrence; Newgatenovelist; Ezwa; fshort; Garth Burton; Greg Giordano; Kit Noussis; Larry Wilson; Leonard Wilson; Maria Kasper; NoelBadrian; Rosslyn Carlyle; Rachel and Vanessa Garcia. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
